metadata.name: glitchy tokenized
metadata.description:
Can you still remember the day you discovered crypto, discovered NFTs, discovered web3.  
I can not. But my short nights have been even shorter since then. New ideas keep popping up in my head. I'm just thinking about what NFT to create next all the time. I'm feeling tired. I feel exhausted. Excited. Happy. I feel tokenized.  
Hopefully anyone who feels the same way is enjoying this NFT as much as I am.

Just a unique glitchy version of my NFT "tokenized" with a short sound loop for the one who likes the pic but doesn´t wan´t to be just one of 100. ;)
